{"tid":1466951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心又偷食】仲有冇人記得許志安，黃心穎？","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:36:00.000Z","uid":297071,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68e55470c3547c09e9d1391116d842d2825c8d30","tid":1466951,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇啊！<br />\n因為612救咗佢。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢件事有咩啓發？<br />\n就係我哋要暫停行動至星期日，畀文宣做嘢！<br />\n機場件事誰是誰非，聽日文宣戰有排打。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過如果事件一單接一單，所有人都消化唔切！<br />\n知唔知我哋點解Sure Win? 因為政府警隊理虧！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n手咁多黑材料喺手，但做嚟做去都估一圍爐文宣。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解？因為對藍、對中立嘅文宣難太多！</span><br />\n要時間度穚，要時間傳畀中立、淺藍。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>所以，係時候行動組休息，畀文宣做嘢，將啲黑材料、事實嘅真相，屌畀啲中立、淺藍，拉佢哋嚟撐住個運動！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">想做實事？我做緊，你呢？<br />\n可以睇我之前兩個post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.【冷氣都有冷氣戰場】Social Marketing/ 真&middot;文宣 你老味！同我吹雞入嚟！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.【緊急！同我推上熱門！！】全港首個FB落AD文宣上線喇！一個藍絲不留！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456295</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59326b6b0ccbf5eda10103394ae6d481416c8657","tid":1466951,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9b01ea86aa61b7d30d8a29eb146bd30e76c5d83","tid":1466951,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1af8b354380064e6f459aaaa4e48d3a36389ab72","tid":1466951,"uid":297071,"like":0,"dislike":0